The `Cytokine` class represents cytokines in the immune response, and here we have used Interleukin-1 (IL-1) as an example. The `ReleaseCytokine()` method signifies the role cytokines play in aiding the white blood cells during an immune response.

In the `Main` method, we have created instances of both white blood cell types and the cytokine, and then demonstrated their defense process, as well as cytokine release through the loop.

